public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y > 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z >= 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;

        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;

    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y > 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y > 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z >= 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;

        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {

    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y > 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y > 0 && x - y - 1 <= 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}

    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));

    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y >= 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z + 1 >= 0 && x - z - 1 <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y >= 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y >= 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z + 1 >= 0 && x - z - 1 <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;

        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {

        }

    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y >= 0 && x - y - 1 <= 10) && (y - z > 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z + 1 >= 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z < 10) && (x - z >= 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z - 1 <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y < 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z + 1 >= 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;

        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {

public class GyroHealthCheck_Original {
    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z > 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z >= 0 && x - z - 1 <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}

    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z < 10) && (x - z >= 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;

    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));

    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y <= 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z + 1 >= 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {

    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y - 1 <= 10) && (y - z > 0 && y - z <= 10) && (x - z >= 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {

    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y - 1 <= 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z < 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z - 1 <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));

    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y - 1 <= 10) && (y - z >= 0 && y - z - 1 <= 10) && (x - z > 0 && x - z < 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {

    //@ ensures \result == 0 || \result == 1;
    //@ ensures \result == 1 ==> ((x - y + 1 >= 0 && x - y - 1 <= 10) && (y - z + 1 >= 0 && y - z < 10) && (x - z + 1 >= 0 && x - z <= 10));  
    //@ ensures \result == 0 ==> ((x - y > 10) || (y - z > 10) || (x - z > 10));
    public static int gyroHealthCheck(int x, int y, int z) {
        int diffXY = x - y;
        if (diffXY < 0) diffXY = -diffXY;
        int diffYZ = y - z;
        if (diffYZ < 0) diffYZ = -diffYZ;
        int diffXZ = x - z;
        if (diffXZ < 0) diffXZ = -diffXZ;
        int alarm = 0;
        if (diffXY > 10 || diffYZ > 10 || diffXZ > 10) {
            alarm = 1;
        }
        return alarm;
    }
}
